Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.38,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'd like a matcha framboise, please.}Một ly framboise trà xanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{You, Komari-chan?}Còn cậu Komari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.91,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Uh, I'll pass.}T-Tôi thì thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.23,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Whoa! It's so good!}Ồ, ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:00.45,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Here. It looks bad, but I haven't touched it.}Nè, nhìn thì hơi nát nhưng tớ chưa đụng vào đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.54,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Are you really sure?}Chắc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:07.00,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, we're here for research. \NIsn't it best if we all eat some?}Thì đang tìm tư liệu mà,\N tất cả phải cùng ăn thử chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.96,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{U-Um, o-okay, thanks.}À ừm... cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.15,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I can't say for sure,}Cảm giác như...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:21.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{but I kinda get the feeling you'd treat me \Na little differently if I was out of money.}cái cách cậu đối xử khác hoàn toàn\N khi tớ không có tiền nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.60,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{If we assume that's true, \Nwould you like me to explain why?}Nếu là vậy thật thì cậu có cần nghe lý do không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.68,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Ow!}Đau!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.31,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{That's what I'm talking about!}Tớ đang nói đến chuyện đó đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.91,Top,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What }{\i1}{are}{\i0}{ you talking about?}Chuyện đó là chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.55,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Th-This is delicious!}N-Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.44,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's}{\i0}{ what I'm talking about!}Chính là chuyện đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.55,Top,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Whoa! Ah! Ouch!}Đau đau!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.02,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna eat another one!}Tớ sẽ ăn thêm!
