Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.62,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an7\blur0.3\fs7\b0\fnGeorgia\fscx82\c&H34434A&\pos(34,135.334)}{Our exhibit will be on the theme of "Edible Readings," and will present \Nour research on foods loved by literary icons and works of literature \Nthat feature food. Additionally, we will sell and pass out snacks related \Nto our research for the visitors' enjoyment. We will also display and sell \Nthe literature club newsletter. This will become an inspiration for literature \Nclub members to write and an opportunity for them to share their work \Nwith a larger audience of readers. The exhibit will also be used as a rest area.}
